    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei et Salvatoris nostri Ihesu Christi, imperantes dominis
                        nostris 
                            Ludovvicus et 
                            Lotharios viros excellentissimos <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                            >augustos</rs>, annis imperii eorum Deo propicio ingrediente
                        terciodecimo et septimo, octavo die mensis februarii, indicione quarta.
                        Commutatio et bone fidei noscitur esse contractus et vicem emptionis
                        obtineat firmitatem eundemque nexum obligat contraentes. Placuit itaque et
                        bone convenit voluntatem inter <persName key="#Commutatio #Bishops #Abbots"
                            ref="#people/1267">Elmericum</persName> reverentissimo <rs
                            key="#Bishops">episcopo</rs> et <rs key="#Abbots">abbate</rs>
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/456"><orgName
                                key="#Monasteries #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/148"
                                >Tollensis</orgName></placeName> nec non et inter <persName
                            key="#Commutatio #Abbots" ref="#people/199">Ansfrit</persName> religioso
                        abbate monasterii <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/15"><orgName
                            key="#Commutatio #Monasteries #Churches #Abbots" ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                                >Nonantule</orgName></placeName> ut in Dei nomine debeat dare, sicut
                        et de presentia dedit his ipse Elmericus episcopum et abbas eidem Ansfredi
                        abbati in causa commutationis, hoc est <rs key="#Churches">basilica</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Houses #Cereals #Rivers #Hay/fodder #Wine"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/1120">Sancte Marie</orgName> in <placeName
                            key="#Churches" ref="#places/1596">Tortilianum</placeName> in <rs
                            key="#Fines">fine</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Fines" ref="#places/1508"><geogName key="#Fines"
                                ref="#estates/1123">Castroferoniense</geogName></placeName> sito cum
                            <rs key="#Houses">casis</rs> et omnibus rebus ad eandem basilicam
                        pertinentibus iuris supranominati monasterii, utis duo milia nongenti et
                        quinquaginta octo inter <rs key="#Cereals">terra arabiles</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Wine">vvidatas</rs> seu <rs key="#Hay/fodder">prativas</rs> iuges
                        sedecim et medium, tabule vigintiquinque et <rs key="#Forests">silva</rs>
                        que est prope ripa <rs key="#Rivers">fluvii</rs> Scultenna in loco
                            <placeName key="#Forests" ref="#places/72">Viniole</placeName> ad saxo
                        iuges quattuor et medium, tabule viginti una, quod fiunt insimul iuges
                        viginti uno, tabule XLVI, et rebus ipsis advenit in eodem monasterio de
                        quendam Elmericum. Idem ad vicem recepit ispe Elmericus episcopus et abbas
                        ab eodem Ansfredo abbate similiter in causa commutacionis, hoc est casis et
                        rebus illis in aliquo, quibus advenit in ipso monasterio de condam
                                <persName><name ref="Garibaldus">Garibalt</name></persName> et sunt
                        positis in loco et fundo <placeName ref="#places/1902">Castro
                            Arcotense</placeName>, loco qui dicitur <placeName
                            key="#Salae #Houses #Chestnuts #Wine #Cereals" ref="#places/1597"
                            >Riocivo</placeName>, in primis <rs key="#Salae">salas muratas</rs> duas
                        ad invicem se copulantes, subter quas et torcular obtime constructum est et
                        canova similiter, utes vero numero tulpos quinque millia centum trigintas et
                        sunt iuges quinque terra seminata una cum sedimen de ipsa casa iuge una, <rs
                            key="#Chestnuts">castaneto</rs> vero et reliqua silva iuges septem,
                        terra arva cum reliquo pasculo iuges quindecim, quod sunt iuges viginti et
                        septem. â€¦ Unde duas cartule scripte sunt. Actum in <placeName
                            ref="#places/1547">Aciu</placeName> feliciter. + Ego Helmericus
                        episcopus in hac commutatione a me facta manu mea subscripsi. + <persName
                            key="#Witness #vassusOf">Rat...</persName> domini imperatoris in hac
                        commutacione rogatus ad Elmericus episcopus <rs key="#Witness #vassusOf"
                            >testis</rs> subscripsi. + <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/1266"
                            >Stephanus</persName>
                        <rs key="#vassusOf">vassus domini imperatoris</rs> in hac commutacione
                        rogatus ad Elmerico episcopo testis subscripsi. + Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Maurus">Mauro</name></persName> in ac cartula
                        commutationis rogatus ad Elmerico episcopo testis subscripsi. + <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Siguvald">Siguvald</name></persName> filius
                                <persName><name ref="Burrus">Buroni</name></persName> in ac
                        commutatione rogatus ab Elmericus episcopum testis subscripsi. + Signum
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Senepertus"
                            >Semperti</name></persName> filius quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannis">Iohannis</name></persName> rogatus testis. + Signum
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Baruncius"
                            >Baruntio</name></persName> filio condam <persName><name ref="Datio"
                                >Dationi</name></persName> rogatus testis. Ego <persName
                            key="#Notary #Writer"><name ref="Radipertus">Ratpertus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>
                        <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> huius commutacionis, quam post traditam
                        complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
